{"tid":1495461,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"24號機場日 - 和你塞 （唔好去觀塘）","createTime":"2019-08-22T05:27:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T06:29:13.000Z","uid":35484,"like":10,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"02fc71eb87ed4fd2dc7c5dee284b342aca5c2753","tid":1495461,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:27:49.000Z","msg":"大家幾時先肯行動升級搞機場？<br />\n搞機場唔單只係搞到香港經濟，亦搞到全世界經濟<br />\n有機場巴絲亦指出，停飛一日全世界要2,3日善後<br />\n大家幾時先肯齊心搞呀？<br />\n唔係搞一日就算 係要成日搞<br />\n港共想攬炒唔志在香港蝕少少 但你覺得咁多受影響既外國公司想唔想蝕？<br />\n全世界陪葬既時候，你覺得啲大國會唔會出聲？<br />\n<br />\n重點係癱瘓機場交通，唔係塞爆機場入面<br />\n空管巴絲返唔到工，航班升降效率低左就會開始delay/cancel架喇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n824觀塘已發不反對通知書<br />\n係驚你地搞機場，唔好中計"},{"pid":"bdf65160051f3d7b6e6ca9aece27297a8856807b","tid":1495461,"uid":67306,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:28:49.000Z","msg":"on9 不嬲都plan左觀塘wo"},{"pid":"424a09b06cd80e8388e02b4b39ddd8d76ae5daf0","tid":1495461,"uid":35484,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:28:51.000Z","msg":"無得起飛 ，交唔切貨 ，賠高額保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勞工保，要claim (因為有衝突有工傷）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貨物鮮貨濕貨 賠償額極高<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有 旅客來自全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以全世界報紙一定出頭條 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後搞到旅客3日番唔到家<br />\n才有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n使鬼你地班on9眾籌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出報紙文宣"},{"pid":"a0527807e88017bd4731026fcb3a3b34bd7266d1","tid":1495461,"uid":120308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":